  - "[Covalent Bonds in Complex Covalent Molecules]\r\n\n\u2022Some atoms need to
    share more than one pair of electrons to gain a full outer shell of electrons\r\n"
  - "\u2022If two adjacent atoms share two pairs of electrons, two covalent bonds
    are formed, also known as a double bond\r\n\n\n\u2022If two adjacent atoms share
    three pairs of electrons, three covalent bonds are formed, also known as a triple
    bond\r\n"
